{"word":"G2225 - ζωογονέω - zōogonéō - dzo-og-on-eh'-o - Live","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ζωογονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">zōogonéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dzo-og-on-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Live</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இரட்சி, உயிரோடிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bring forth alive"},{"paragraph":"2. to give life"},{"paragraph":"3. to preserve alive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2226 - ζῶον - zōon - dzo'-on/2226\">G2226</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1096 - γίνομαι - gínomai - ghin'-om-ahee/1096\">G1096</a>; to <i>engender alive</i> that is, (by analogy) to <i>rescue</i> (passively <i>be saved</i>) from death: - live, preserve.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1186/1186\">G1186</a>, <a href=\"#/G2198/2198\">G2198</a>, <a href=\"#/G2222/2222\">G2222</a>, <a href=\"#/G2225/2225\">G2225</a>, <a href=\"#/G2226/2226\">G2226</a>, <a href=\"#/G2227/2227\">G2227</a>, <a href=\"#/G326/326\">G326</a>"}]}